import numpy as np
import cmath

def solve_quadratic(a, b, c):
    disc = b ** 2 + 4 * a * c
    root1 = (-b - cmath.sqrt(disc)) / (2 * a)
    root2 = (-b + cmath.sqrt(disc)) / (2 * a)
    return (root1, root2)

def evaluate_quadratic(a, b, c, x_range):
    p = np.poly1d([a, b, c])
    values = np.polyval(p, x_range)
    return values
